    • Method Detail

      • call

        ClosingFuture<V> call(ClosingFuture.DeferredCloser closer,
                      ClosingFuture.Peeker peeker)
               throws Exception
        Computes a ClosingFuture result, or throws an exception if unable to do so.

        Any objects that are passed to closer.eventuallyClose() will be closed when the ClosingFuture pipeline is done (but not before this method completes), even if this method throws or the pipeline is cancelled.

        Parameters:
        peeker - used to get the value of any of the input futures
        Throws:
        Exception
